.\" -*- nroff -*-
.TH NORDUGRIDMAP 8 "@DATE@" "NorduGrid ARC @VERSION@" "NorduGrid System Managers Manual"
.SH NAME
nordugridmap \- ARC grid-mapfile generator
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B nordugridmap
[\fB-t\fR, \fB--test\fR] [\fB-c\fR, \fB--config\fR \fIFILE\fR] [\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
nordugridmap is usually run as a crontab entry in order to automatically generate mapfile(s). For configuration information consult the arc.conf.template
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-test\fR
Print the filter generated from the configuration file and other debug informations including used configuration settings. In this case the grid-mapfile(s) is not created.
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-config \fIFILE\fR
Specifies the configuration file, by the default the /etc/arc.conf is used. nordugridmap processes all the [vo] blocks from the arc.conf.
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Show help options
.PP
.SH REPORTING BUGS
Report bugs to http://bugzilla.nordugrid.org/

